description: Oh jeez, you probably have a pretty severe case of the munchies after a full day of beachy fun. Good thing the wheels on this bus are serving delicious tropical meals all around Corpus Christi!Taking Spanish fusion cuisine and giving it a tropical twist, their menu features a tasty, eclectic selection of Street Tacos: (Chicken, steak, or pork with lettuce, cheese, and tomatoes) and Sandwiches, such as their the Cubano Kush (Roasted pork, black forest ham, Swiss cheese, dill pickles, and house-made honey mustard), Pineapple Express (Signature chicken, pineapple & mango salsa, provolone, and pineapple aioli), OG Philly Mac (Thinly sliced steak or chicken, sauteed peppers and onions, queso blanco, and homemade mac & Cheese), to name a few. So get your next foodie fix at the Munchies Bus...because we’ll be blunt, this food is dope.
name: Munchies Bus
